\c 87 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 87\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Jajata Yerusaalem (Faarfannaa ilmaan Qoraahi; weedduu)
\m \bd 1\bd* Mandarri Waaqayyo hundee ishee kaa'e, tulloota qulqullaa'oo gubbaa in dhaabatti.
\m \bd 2\bd* Waaqayyo iddoo buufata Yaaqoob hundumaa caalaa mandara Xiyoon karra ishee wajjin in jaallata.
\m \bd 3\bd* Yaa mandara Waaqayyoo, wanti ulfina-qabeessi waa'ee keef in dubbatama.
\m \bd 4\bd* "Rahaab-Gibxii fi Baabilonin warra ana beekanitti nan lakkaa'a, ilaa, warri Filisxiyaa, warri Xiiroos, warri Itoophiyaas akka warra achitti dhalataniitti fudhataman" in jedhama.
\m \bd 5\bd* Waa'ee Xiyooniifis, "Namni kun, namni sunis, ishee keessatti in dhalate, aabba inni hundumaa gararraa jirus jabeessee ishee dhaabeera" in jedhama.
\m \bd 6\bd* Waaqayyo maqaa saba lafa irraa yeroo caafus, "Warri kun achitti dhalatan" in jedha.
\m \bd 7\bd* Warri faarfatanii fi warri weeddisaa naanna'an, "Wanti hundinuu si biraa anaaf in burqa" jedhanii wal jalaa in qabu.
\b 
